Package com.casioeurope.mis.edt.constant

Class EDTLibraryConstant.METHOD

Object
METHOD
Enclosing class:
EDTLibraryConstant
public static class EDTLibraryConstant.METHOD
extends Object
Methods of the EDTLibrary class, used e.g. to check availability of said methods using EDTLibrary.isMethodSupported(BigInteger) method.
